          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>July 4<hi rend="sup">th</hi> / 53</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>My Dear Friend,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">As I see by last Occident the Bible<lb/> is
                                        progressing, I wish you to remember
                                                  <persName>Rehine's</persName> wish<lb/> that I
                                        should have one of the best, I wish such<lb/> binding as my
                                                  <hi rend="underline">set</hi> if you recollect,
                                        also <del>a book</del><lb/> wish to know what a <hi
                                                  rend="underline">set</hi> of neat small size
                                        a<lb/> wit<hi rend="underline">ho</hi>ut d<hi
                                                  rend="underline">ai</hi>ly, would cost for
                                                  <persName>Herman</persName>, if you<lb/> have
                                        them, also let me know, what the “Leper &amp; other<lb/>
                                        Poems” cost; I would thank you to make such<lb/> selections
                                        as your <hi rend="underline">good</hi>
                                        <sic>Judgement</sic> suggests<lb/> of <persName>Miss
                                                  Aguilar's</persName> works, I have Jewish Faith,
                                        &amp; home<lb/> Influence, the Essays &amp; miscellanies I
                                        think perhaps<lb/> would be useful for
                                                  <persName>Josephine</persName> let me know<lb/>
                                        what “Vale of Ceaders” and <hi rend="underline">it</hi> will
                                        cost with any you think best.
                                        <persName>Rehine</persName><lb/> writes I may have what
                                        works I like, still<lb/> I do not wish to Tax him Too far—I
                                        wish<lb/> you'd please have my name on outside<lb/> Bible
                                        with from “son <persName>Rehine</persName>” I have just
                                        written<lb/> a letter to our dear Friend <persName>E
                                                  Moses</persName>, to come on<lb/> with
                                                  <persName>Mr Block</persName>, whom I expect soon,
                                                  <persName>Rosalie</persName><lb/> &amp; family
                                        spend the summer with <persName>Lucia</persName>,
                                                  (<sic>untill</sic><lb/> after her marriage, which
                                        you no doubt are<lb/> informed
                                                  of—<persName>Eleanor</persName> has gone to
                                                  <placeName>Arkansas</placeName> to<lb/> Cousin
                                                  <persName><sic>Franzs</sic></persName>
                                        <persName>Sarah</persName> is with the rest at
                                                  <placeName>Quincy</placeName><lb/>
                                        <persName>Abraham</persName> &amp; my Husband go in business
                                        at <placeName>Memphis</placeName><lb/> do let me know the
                                        state of the Jews if you<lb/> know there as I feel reluctant
                                        to go out of congregite<add>?</add></p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>have the Shoket &amp;c—give my love to <persName>Aunt<lb/>
                                                  Marks</persName> tell her I was up at
                                                  <persName>Aunt <sic>Beckys</sic></persName><lb/>
                                        yesterday Aunty's 81<hi rend="sup">st</hi> birthday she
                                        looks well<lb/> altho' complains of her eyes—also best
                                        regards<lb/> to <persName>Mr Mrs Florence</persName> and
                                                  <persName>Allen</persName> and all
                                                  <sic>enquiring</sic><lb/> friends—I saw the new
                                        importation of <persName>Seixas'</persName><lb/> his Father
                                        stayed with us in <placeName>Richmond</placeName> he is very
                                        <lb/>like him—write soon—hope your health<lb/> is better and
                                        that I shall soon<lb/> hear a very <hi rend="underline"
                                                  >desirable</hi> piece of news the<lb/> Union of my
                                        good friend <persName>Isaac</persName> with some<lb/>
                                        amiable girl—<persName>Mrs David Cohen</persName> and
                                                  <persName>'Coll<lb/> Cohen</persName> with two
                                        daughters have gone to <placeName>Europe</placeName><lb/>
                                        all send love; shall we see you here<lb/> soon? good bye
                                        your friend ever <persName role="author"
                                        >Ablock</persName></p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>
                                                  <hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi>
                                        </placeName>
                              </p>
